title: Seed Swap
location: Small Wonders Farm, 1370 Siloam Church Rd, Westmoreland, TN 37186, USA
description: Bring seeds to share if you have them, but don’t worry if you don’t. We’ve built a strong seed bank and have plenty to share with those who may not have access. Come connect with fellow gardeners, swap knowledge, and get inspired for the growing season ahead.
